      "duration": 1.51,
      "size": 24192,
      "text": "一条线是一维的，一个正方形是二维的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "peano-curve",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/peano-curve/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "可你相信吗，有一条连续的曲线，能不留缝隙地填满整个正方形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "peano-curve",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/peano-curve/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "1890 年，意大利数学家皮亚诺第一个造出了它，震动了整个数学界。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "peano-curve",
      "section_id": "recursion",
      "line_id": "rec-1",
      "filename": "recursion-rec-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/peano-curve/recursion-rec-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.66,
      "size": 26496,
      "text": "把正方形切成三行三列，一共九个小格。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "peano-curve",
      "section_id": "recursion",
      "line_id": "rec-2",
      "filename": "recursion-rec-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/peano-curve/recursion-rec-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.86,
      "size": 45792,
      "text": "曲线按特定顺序依次穿过这九格，并在每一格里重复同样的九宫格花样。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "peano-curve",
      "section_id": "recursion",
      "line_id": "rec-3",
      "filename": "recursion-rec-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/peano-curve/recursion-rec-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.05,
      "size": 32832,
      "text": "每提升一阶，格点数就变成九倍，曲线越来越密。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "peano-curve",
      "section_id": "hilbert",
      "line_id": "hil-3",
      "filename": "hilbert-hil-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/peano-curve/hilbert-hil-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.71,
      "size": 43344,
      "text": "希尔伯特曲线相邻点在原空间也相邻，因此更常用于图像和数据索引。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "peano-curve",
      "section_id": "interaction",
